text: Kalaktang is a town in the Indian state of Arunachal Pradesh West Kameng is the name of the district that contains town Kalaktang. Kalaktang is one of the 60 constituencies of Legislative Assembly of Arunachal Pradesh. Name of current MLA (May-2019) of this constituency is Mr. Dorjee Wangdi Kharma.
